fields.message: You can use {% for message in messages reversed %} to ensure the messages are displayed from the most recent to the oldest.

Option 1: Ensure Messages Are Ordered in the View
In your Django view, make sure the messages are ordered by the timestamp field in ascending order (oldest to newest). This way, when you iterate through the messages in your template, they are already in the correct order:
